title: Fallout Shelter v1.6.1
description: is a free-to-play mobile simulation video game developed by Bethesda Game Studios, with assistance by Behaviour Interactive, and published by Bethesda Softworks. Part of the Fallout series, it was released worldwide for iOS devices in June 2015, for Android devices in August 2015, and for Microsoft Windows in July 2016. The game tasks the player with building and managing their own Vault, a fallout shelter
